1. *Metara* od nas je potrebno da odemo doma. (One meter away from us is needed for us to go home.)
2. On je skočio više od dve *metare*. (He jumped more than two meters.)
3. Ona je bacila loptu preko deset *metara*. (She threw the ball over ten meters.)
4. Pružio je ruku preko tri *metra*. (He stretched his hand over three meters.)
5. Udaljenost između njih je pet *metara*. (The distance between them is five meters.)
6. Preko *metra* snega je bilo na putu. (Over a meter of snow was on the road.)